### Get All Customers
GET http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/customers

###
### Get Customer with ID 1
GET http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/customers/1

###
### Create a New Customer
POST http://localhost:8081/pahana-edu-api/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountNumber": "CUST-003",
  "fullName": "Alice Williams",
  "address": "789 Pine Lane",
  "city": "Oakville",
  "postalCode": "54321",
  "phoneNumber": "555-0103",
  "email": "alice.w@example.com"
}

